{"tid":2178244,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[中国武漢肺炎]Foodpanda外賣員確診","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:10.000Z","uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf7fe9c8943038c1ac383cb575eca43ae5fd024","tid":2178244,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"本港疫情未止，衞生防護中心公布今日（28日）新增13宗確診個案，3宗為輸入個案，其餘10宗為本地感染病例。本地感染個案，當中有7宗與早前個案相關，當中4宗與家庭、朋友聚會相關，3宗源頭不明。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，3宗源頭不明個案中，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">包括一名54歲Foodpanda女外賣員（個案編號：4762），於將軍澳工作</span></span>；一名是學生和一名於港景峰工作的地產經紀（個案編號：4764）。<br />\n<br />\n她指，該名外賣員工作時有戴手套，故客人不會視為緊密接觸者，她亦涉及一個家庭群組共3人確診，而最早病發是該外賣員，故定義為無源頭，其中兒子體內有抗體，有機會才是源頭，需要再調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2737953/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91Foodpanda%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E3%80%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%AC%9D%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2737953%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591Foodpanda%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2589%2580%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=b18ad4d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2737953/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91Foodpanda%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E3%80%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%AC%9D%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳叫外賣個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}